<content>
    <para id="id16219044">There are two general classes of carbon halides. </para>
    <list id="id16047166" list-type="enumerated" number-style="arabic">
      <item>Homoleptic halides, e.g., CCl<sub>4</sub>, CCl<sub>2</sub>F<sub>2</sub>, C<sub>6</sub>Cl<sub>6</sub>, etc. </item>
      <item>Carbonyl halides, e.g., Cl<sub>2</sub>C=O. </item>
    </list>
    <para id="id16336040">A summary of some simple carbon halides is given in <link target-id="id19569057"/>. </para>



